69ab2e70f9b0618dafb170236988d0b","tid":1381961,"uid":25272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:01:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">香港人已經退無可退，而共匪亦已無計可施，我哋必須要團結一致打贏呢場仗！香港發動罷工從來不易，唯靠各路英雄廣傳推動！！！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U1BBO2R.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU1BBO2R.png&h=7b6de41f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wo2A4Bc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwo2A4Bc.png&h=aece6a07&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uxhmfHT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuxhmfHT.png&h=7bd927da&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hZogO2T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhZogO2T.png&h=39414509&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q8HQTuz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ8HQTuz.png&h=77594675&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KdH9pBe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKdH9pBe.png&h=13867443&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eMKDhWe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeMKDhWe.png&h=b1941320&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELOE9A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELOE9A.png&h=716067a6&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:09:19.000Z","msg":"【中學生的聲音】<br />\n<br />\n我哋雖然年紀小，但都希望盡全力發出最大嘅聲音。<br />\n<br />\n學生係未來社會嘅棟樑，所以我哋都有必要為自己，為大家發聲。<br />\n<br />\n雖然呢次係香港最分化嘅一次,但亦都係香港人最團結嘅一次。而我哋中學生都想令大家更團結，所以搞咗今次嘅聯署。<br />\n<br />\n【中學生聯署計劃】<br />\n<br />\n民主運動從來都係先由中學生、大學生發起，因為我哋有一股傻勁，我哋雖然會有衝動嘅時候，但全因為我哋對未來總係抱有無限嘅理想，更願意為理想而付出。<br />\n<br />\n我哋嘅堅持已經令而家好多喺政府部門嘅大人都出咗聲啦，今次就到我哋中學生一齊集氣，比呢個不公義嘅政府聽聽，屬於香港人真正嘅聲音！<br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以係表中填上你嘅學校名，同遮蓋重要個人資料嘅學生證，一齊加入聯署！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdz5V_o8_YiWRVqSsNi9tP1abAHkU0cd7TYr69r1wO1_GyFSA/viewform?usp=pp_url\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdz5V_o8_YiWRVqSsNi9tP1abAHkU0cd7TYr69r1wO1_GyFSA%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dpp_url&d=SfvWO4iieP9%2B5ivoSMB2BrTKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=8f4e454b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdz5V_o8_YiWRVqSsNi9tP1abAHkU0cd7TYr69r1wO1_GyFSA/viewform?usp=pp_url</a><br />\n<br />\n【A Petition from Secondary School Students for the Solidarity of All Hongkongers]<br />\n<br />\nThe voice of us:<br />\n<br />\nAlthough we are only secondary school students, we try our best to speak up. <br />\n<br />\nStudents are the future pillars of the society, and it is necessary for us to fight for the future and our next generation. <br />\n<br />\nHong Kong is now the most divided, yet Hongkongers are at the same time the most united that we have never seen before.<br />\n<br />\nWe hope we can use our power to make Hongkongers more united, so we initiate this petition.<br />\n<br />\nWe are secondary school students, we want to make the world a better place! <br />\n<br />\nPlease sign:<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdz5V_o8_YiWRVqSsNi9tP1abAHkU0cd7TYr69r1wO1_GyFSA/viewform?usp=pp_url\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdz5V_o8_YiWRVqSsNi9tP1abAHkU0cd7TYr69r1wO1_GyFSA%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dpp_url&d=SfvWO4iieP9%2B5ivoSMB2BrTKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=8f4e454b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdz5V_o8_YiWRVqSsNi9tP1abAHkU0cd7TYr69r1wO1_GyFSA/viewform?usp=pp_url</a><br />\n<br />\n#民主路。有你有我，缺一不可"},{"pid":"e813dcfd1089db42058f42ea55582549aede606e","tid":1381961,"uid":25272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:15